% Bandas centrais de 1/3 de oitava [Hz]
fc = [1 1.25 1.6 2 2.5 3.15 4 5 6.3 8 10 12.5 16 20 25 31.5 40 50 63 80];

f1 = fc / (2^(1/6));
f2 = fc * (2^(1/6));

